        "subject": "Additional Information Required - FinServe",
        "message": "=<div style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto;\">\n<p>Dear <strong>{{ $('On form submission').first().json['Applicant Name'] }}</strong>,</p>\n<p>Thank you for your interest in FinServe lending services.</p>\n<p>We have completed an initial review and are pleased to move forward. However, to complete our assessment, we require the following documents:</p>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;\">\n<tr style=\"background:#003366; color:white;\">\n<td><strong>Application Details</strong></td><td></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Company</strong></td>\n<td>{{ $('On form submission').first().json['Company Name'] }}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\">\n<td><strong>Loan Amount</strong></td>\n<td>{{ $('On form submission').first().json['Currency'] }} {{ $('On form submission').first().json['Loan Amount Requested'] }}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><strong>Country</strong></td>\n<td>{{ $('On form submission').first().json['Country'] }}</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"background:#f9f9f9;\">\n<td><strong>Status</strong></td>\n<td>⏳ PENDING — Documents Required</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<br>\n<table border=\"1\" cellpadding=\"10\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:collapse; width:100%;\">\n<tr style=\"background:#003366; color:white;\">\n<td><strong>Required Documents</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>{{ $('Code1').first().json.Required_docs }}</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<br>\n<p>Please submit within <strong>7 business days</strong> to avoid delays.</p>\n<p>Reply to this email or contact: <a href=\"mailto:support@finserve.com\">support@finserve.com</a></p>\n<p>We look forward to supporting your business growth.</p>\n<p>Warm regards,<br>\n<strong>FinServe Credit Team</strong><br>\n📧 support@finserve.com<br>\n🌐 www.finserve.com</p>\n</div>",
        "options": {}
