cific reason based on given data only]\nReapply After: 6 months\n\nIf Decision is MORE_INFO_NEEDED:\nRequired Documents:\n- [Country specific compliance document 1]\n- [Country specific compliance document 2]\n- [Based on business type - be specific]\n- [Based on loan amount - be specific]\n- [Based on risk level - be specific]\n\nCountry specific requirements:\nIndia: GST returns 2 years, ITR last 2 years, \n       MSME certificate if applicable,\n       6 months bank statements\n\nUSA: Federal tax returns 2 years,\n     EIN verification letter,\n     Business license copy,\n     6 months bank statements\n\nEurope/France: VAT registration certificate,\n               EU business license,\n               IBAN bank details,\n               6 months bank statements\n\nPoland: NIP number verification,\n        ZUS registration document,\n        VAT-7 declaration last 2 years,\n        6 months bank statements\n\nFollow up: Our credit team will contact \nwithin 3 business days.\n\nCredit Officer: FinServe AI System"
